programme.desc: 花蘋提出跟蹤漢斯搜證；花蘋會合三人，憐香不禁好奇花蘋表現專業……羅帛緊隨呂芳，只覺她與Richard關係不簡單。花蘋遇上羅帛，羅帛請她給意見。羅帛約大樹要他與女友慶祝周年紀念，更為他準備了節目清單。

programme.title: 錦心似玉#20[粵/普][PG]
programme.desc: 喬家安插在仙綾閣的人挑撥繡娘，十一娘被控欺壓災民，被太夫人看見。十一娘假孕暴露，太夫人大怒，十一娘指控蓮房卻無證據，反被指犯了七出之條。喬母在外散播十一娘打著永平侯旗號欺壓災民一事，終令令宜寫下休書。

programme.title: 深夜美食團[粵]
programme.desc: 主持們和歐倩怡、梁雪湄在客棧主題餐廳相聚，翻開「武功秘笈」，一試各款滋味小菜。倩怡分享與丈夫郭晉安當年擦出愛火的韓國拍攝之旅，又提到子女哼唱其經典兒歌，卻不知道媽媽是原唱者的趣事。美食團帶湯怡往中菜餐廳，享用意想不到的新派融合菜。湯怡提到會在電影飾演學生，卻被主持連番追問其男友洪卓立，不禁「發火」！百年老字號甜品店的中式傳統糖水，遠近馳名。老闆推介招牌「桑寄生蓮子蛋茶」，並憶述過往招待明星的點滴。

programme.title: 深夜美食團[粵]
programme.desc: 「星級」老闆黃長興在尖沙咀開設第二間法國餐廳，內裡裝潢更情商好友雷頌德精心設計。長興誠邀美食團前來新店試菜，並分享創業與守業的心得。向來親力親為的長興還即席下廚，帶來由母親真傳的秘製炒青口。主持們及後相約關楚耀、「大埔LuLu」董嘉儀到蒸氣石鍋店，享用海鮮大餐之外，亦品嚐蒸氣鍋底層、吸盡海鮮精華的粥底，極盡鮮甜！楚耀細說在台灣發展飲食業的契機。LuLu原來「入得廚房」，難道是靠廚藝俘虜男友的心？

programme.desc: 參賽者返回廚神廚房，進行第三次出菜挑戰。今次應戰的專業廚師團隊來自著名餐廳Lucy Liu。今次雙方要採用指定食材，去製作三道菜。之前勝出的團隊都是在自己的主場比賽，今次廚神隊又是否有主場之利？

programme.desc: 來到高手過招最後一戰。餘下的四位參賽者要跟傑森斯托特在他主理的餐廳Stokehouse對決，爭取下次淘汰賽的豁免權。兩隊要決定今晚三道菜式的主要顏色，並在兩個半小時後把既美味而又能突出顏色的前菜端出。

programme.title: 紅色高踭鞋#2[粵/韓][PG]
programme.desc: 貞國目睹熙瓊和赫相一起去蛋糕店，一怒之下把生病的熙瓊趕出家門。絕望的熙瓊打電話向赫相求助，赫相便立刻開車去找她。貞國酒醒後懊悔不已，也出門找熙瓊，卻被赫相的車撞到。玉璟想把實情告知警方，卻被太吉阻止…

programme.title: 日常生活搶知識[粵/日]
programme.desc: 世界上充滿了古老的民間傳說、神秘的都市傳聞和有趣的故事，來做個驗證找出答案！

programme.title: 北歐潮什麼[粵]
programme.desc: 冰島一款牛奶朱古力榮獲世界級的朱古力獎項，芷佩大手入貨，還深入廠房揭開出產美味朱古力的竅門。她兼職一日員工，學做自創口味的朱古力，更獲老闆親自調製朱古力熱飲，味道有多獨特？一間開業數十年的熱狗店，經常大排長龍，芷佩「打孖」享用這款國民美食，還強調醬汁、配料全加，才最滋味！雷克霍特的天然熔岩洞穴，帶來特色的探索體驗，芷佩發現甚麼奇趣東西，不禁要出手摸？她又推介抵食餐廳，品嚐鮮甜龍蝦湯、滑嫩烤魚肉串。

programme.title: 出走地圖[粵/普]
programme.desc: 主持梁凱晴初到加拿大溫哥華，找來熟悉當地的娛樂主播郭浩皇充當導遊。第一站到訪手工掃把店，見識不同造型、功能的掃把，其中一款專為結婚而設？在名信片專賣店搜羅當地藝術家的作品，送禮不失禮。坐在碼頭吹着海風，享用甜品、小食，好Chill。雪糕店供應逾百種口味，教人花多眼亂，榴槤曲奇餅、大蒜等重口味如何衝擊味蕾？一間主打多國小品牌的服裝店是浩皇的心頭好，有甚麼獨特潮品？西四大道的翅膀壁畫，更是打卡首選！

programme.title: 黃金庭院#18[粵/韓]
programme.desc: 俊基覺得南熙身體不對勁,從秀美口中得知楠熙舊病復發。東珠帶了信任兄妹到崔家玩耍,Sabrina看見信任大為震驚,覺得東珠故意陷害自己, 要俊基開除她, 俊基以東珠要照顧南熙為由拒絕。Sabrina向蘭淑求助。

programme.title: 網紅甜卡[粵]
programme.desc: Christy、Jessica進行街訪，探討巴黎人的早餐文化，接著往麵包店選購特色麵包及甜品，與Veronica在巴黎鐵塔下的戰神廣場野餐、打卡。Veronica預備的貝雷帽份外搶鏡，配戴時有甚麼需注意？她還分享打卡技巧。三人更拆解迷思，嘗試法國風味把牛角包浸泡咖啡來吃，會否中伏？兩位主持造訪巴黎最古老的糕點店及其姊妹朱古力店，試吃鎮店甜品「Rum baba」、朱古力放題……美食背後有甚麼故事？

programme.title: 不如食豪D[粵]
programme.desc: 繼續同嘉賓曾比特「食豪D」，尚友這次會以白松露製作街頭甜吃「雞蛋仔」；還會用上本地出產的龍眼蜜糖，因為產量少，所以珍貴。除了雞蛋仔，連同上集的兩款雞肉美食，開餐！比特不小心把雞翼掉到地上，6號願將另一隻雞翼相贈，但條件是要他「供出」初戀情報。回味初吻時，比特不自覺咬叉子？6號找來一幅比特少年時期參加歌唱比賽的照片，竟與尚友有幾分相似？比特又分享成為爆炸頭的經過，原來最初只是想模仿攣毛韓仔？

programme.title: 關注關注組[粵]
programme.desc: 這次關注居酒屋話題，黃嘉雯自揭曾到訪日式居酒屋約會，覺得內裡氣氛更有助談心。她又提到日本有居酒屋提供掌摑顧客服務，竟然大受歡迎！「日行」前往台式居酒屋實習，除了學習準備「薑汁番茄」、「厚切牛腱」等佐酒小食之外，也會嘗試斟啤酒，原來並不簡單？焯日預備大麥啤酒、西柚燒酌等，讓大本營「變身」居酒屋，怎料全都是零酒精飲品？他還「叮」了燒鰻魚串、醬油牛肉飯團等多款佐酒小吃，拍檔們嚐味後可會「收貨」？

programme.title: 紅色高踭鞋#2[粵/韓][PG]
programme.desc: 貞國目睹熙瓊和赫相一起去蛋糕店，一怒之下把生病的熙瓊趕出家門。絕望的熙瓊打電話向赫相求助，赫相便立刻開車去找她。貞國酒醒後懊悔不已，也出門找熙瓊，卻被赫相的車撞到。玉璟想把實情告知警方，卻被太吉阻止…

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵][PG]
programme.desc: 藝人樊亦敏與道教正一派師傅張羅暉，因交流道教知識而結緣。今回二人帶來關於「惡妖追債」的神秘個案，暉師傅還會講述正一派的起源。暉師傅在聚會中察覺到好友A君遭黑氣纏身，追查下得悉其因為助人而受牽連；後來又揭發另一男子遭惡妖施咒，身患重病。暉師傅即請「祖師」守護男子，終令惡妖妥協並且順利度過七日關鍵期。未料事後竟突然傳出男子病逝消息，到底所為何事？暉師傅還道出「撞鬼」的三大分類，以及咒術如何加害於人。

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵][PG]
programme.desc: 為了祈願求福，而佩戴來歷不明的佛牌，隨時惹禍上身！藝人樊亦敏、道家師傅張羅暉強調佛牌應依正途恭請，亦提到供奉佛牌或須付出代價！亦敏引述朋友工作不順，忽獲老闆送贈「運財佛牌」得以改善困局。友人及後為照顧家庭決心轉行，未料常發惡夢，氣息越來越差，他求助某師傅後更發現禍端來自運財佛牌？另一男事主事事不順，得某師傅提醒在家中尋回遺忘多年的佛牌；惟當佛牌被燒毀之後，男事主竟慘遭「五鬼纏繞」，情況有多可怕？

programme.title: 姊妹淘[粵]
programme.desc: 在秋冬時分，乾燥的天氣會令皮膚失去水份，所以姊妹們要加強保養及保濕的意識。兩位港姐冠軍葉翠翠與張嘉兒不單擁有美貌與智慧，更有著滑溜溜的好皮膚，令人羨慕。原來她們也有一些獨門的美容心得，葉翠翠在秋冬時會使用護膚油，令肌膚得到更多滋潤，而張嘉兒和主持莊思敏則同樣有著鼻敏感的問題，她們有甚麼妙法解決呢？另外，內在的調理亦絕不能忽視，想擁有好膚質，必定要內外夾撃！現時許多化妝品都有兩用的特色，莊思敏就介紹一枝兩用唇彩，它不但可以用於嘴唇之上，亦可當作胭脂使用，非常方便。

programme.title: 開端#3[粵/普]
programme.desc: 遊戲架構師肖鶴雲和女大學生李詩情在公交車爆炸的交通事故後「死而復生」，陷入時間循環。他們於密閉空間自救、努力阻止爆炸，並尋找出兇手才能結束循環。

programme.title: 鎮鄉之寶[粵/普]
programme.desc: 世界馳名的瑞士手錶，只佔全球產量2%，價值卻佔市場一半。本集君偉帶大家前往瑞士汝拉山脈，參觀鐘錶小鎮勒洛克勒，了解機械錶的歷史。然後認識掐絲琺瑯技藝，走訪製錶大師和維修及保養古董鐘的三父子，萬勿錯過。

programme.title: 夢想改造家[粵]
programme.desc: 節目突破以色彩和軟裝為主的傳統裝修形式，聚焦於空間改變和功能實現上。由頂尖設計師以有限的資金，在有限的空間裡，根據委託人的特殊需求進行徹底改造。通過設計師的匠心巧思，完成看似不可能的家裝夢想。

programme.title: MUSIC BREAK[粵]
programme.desc: 本集由趙頌宜Maggie(@c_chungyee_)推介歌單，播放的MV包括「勁歌金榜No.2」馮允謙《給你幸福 所以幸福》、陳奕迅《空城記》、陳明憙《Little Love》、Twins《雙喜樓》、吳業坤《分手前中後》；林子祥、劉德華《難為正邪定分界》；Gareth.T《緊急聯絡人》。

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵]
programme.desc: 歌手出身的胡諾言（胡仔）接棒成為《流行經典50年》主持，多年後再於一廠舞台展露歌喉。他大表幸福，還形容熟悉的感覺「翻晒嚟」！胡仔當年在歌唱比賽奪冠，繼而進軍樂壇，備受唱片公司力捧，還得著名經理人小美為其設計形象，前途一片光明。可惜遇上97年金融風暴及盜版猖獗打擊，胡仔未能突圍，只好轉戰電視圈。他提到曾重遊昔日常往錄歌的錄音室訪問歌手，面對身分的轉變，心中不禁難受！他如何逐漸釋懷，樂觀面對人生挫折？

programme.title: 兄弟幫[粵]
programme.desc: 胡諾言（胡仔）加入《流行經典50年》主持陣容，重踏久違的歌唱舞台，還有機會跟兩位前輩黎小田、薛家燕搭檔，感受如何？胡仔大讚小田哥風趣，並得到大師提點音樂技巧，獲益良多！他又提到家燕姐猶如媽媽般，對拍檔們照顧有加，合作時特別輕鬆。胡仔既是三名子女之父，亦是馬拉松發燒友，工作、家庭等各方面怎樣分配？這位好爸爸還會細述照顧子女的日程，雖然忙碌，卻樂在其中！胡仔更披露在熱播劇《特技人》裡有裸跑演出……

programme.title: 北歐潮什麼[粵]
programme.desc: 遊冰島，必到地標藍湖泡溫泉。置身牛奶藍色的泉水，遠眺迷人雪景，並享用免費飲品及敷面膜，絕對是夢幻級享受！「梳乎」過後，芷珮回首都搜購特色手信，除了浴鹽、冰石等人氣商品外，還可購買當地的新鮮空氣？一間農場連咖啡廳，採用自動化機器飼養牛牛，芷珮進內細看自動餵食、自動擠奶等機器的運作，並品嚐新鮮牛奶、奶昔。奇趣的陰莖博物館，教芷珮大開眼界！各款陰莖手信或許太另類？芷珮轉往超市介紹較大眾化的朱古力和醬汁。

programme.title: 出走地圖[粵/普] 及 勞資守法保職安[粵]
programme.desc: 梁凱晴、牟韻潔前往「溫哥華心臟」Stanley Park觀賞楓葉景色、細探原住民圖騰柱，還可一見獅門大橋的壯麗面貌。位於北溫哥華的特色市場有逾八十間商戶，嚐過超大奶昔後，再走進老字號糖果店，才算滿足。市場旁邊的碼頭，更是欣賞夕陽的好地方！來到Fort Langley小鎮，可發掘各式各樣的古董與生活用品，主持們盡情「尋寶」！小紅莓亦是當地特產，還會製成食醋、調味粉。去旅行當然要逛超市，有何必買手信？

programme.title: 黃金庭院#18[粵/韓]
programme.desc: 俊基覺得南熙身體不對勁,從秀美口中得知楠熙舊病復發。東珠帶了信任兄妹到崔家玩耍,Sabrina看見信任大為震驚,覺得東珠故意陷害自己, 要俊基開除她, 俊基以東珠要照顧南熙為由拒絕。Sabrina向蘭淑求助。

programme.title: 不如食豪D[粵]
programme.desc: 繼續同嘉賓曾比特「食豪D」，尚友這次會以白松露製作街頭甜吃「雞蛋仔」；還會用上本地出產的龍眼蜜糖，因為產量少，所以珍貴。除了雞蛋仔，連同上集的兩款雞肉美食，開餐！比特不小心把雞翼掉到地上，6號願將另一隻雞翼相贈，但條件是要他「供出」初戀情報。回味初吻時，比特不自覺咬叉子？6號找來一幅比特少年時期參加歌唱比賽的照片，竟與尚友有幾分相似？比特又分享成為爆炸頭的經過，原來最初只是想模仿攣毛韓仔？

programme.title: 關注關注組[粵]
programme.desc: 這次關注居酒屋話題，黃嘉雯自揭曾到訪日式居酒屋約會，覺得內裡氣氛更有助談心。她又提到日本有居酒屋提供掌摑顧客服務，竟然大受歡迎！「日行」前往台式居酒屋實習，除了學習準備「薑汁番茄」、「厚切牛腱」等佐酒小食之外，也會嘗試斟啤酒，原來並不簡單？焯日預備大麥啤酒、西柚燒酌等，讓大本營「變身」居酒屋，怎料全都是零酒精飲品？他還「叮」了燒鰻魚串、醬油牛肉飯團等多款佐酒小吃，拍檔們嚐味後可會「收貨」？

programme.title: 開端#3[粵/普]
programme.desc: 遊戲架構師肖鶴雲和女大學生李詩情在公交車爆炸的交通事故後「死而復生」，陷入時間循環。他們於密閉空間自救、努力阻止爆炸，並尋找出兇手才能結束循環。

programme.title: 紅色高踭鞋#2[粵/韓][PG]
programme.desc: 貞國目睹熙瓊和赫相一起去蛋糕店，一怒之下把生病的熙瓊趕出家門。絕望的熙瓊打電話向赫相求助，赫相便立刻開車去找她。貞國酒醒後懊悔不已，也出門找熙瓊，卻被赫相的車撞到。玉璟想把實情告知警方，卻被太吉阻止…

programme.title: 網紅甜卡[粵] 及 勞資守法保職安[粵]
programme.desc: Christy、Jessica進行街訪，探討巴黎人的早餐文化，接著往麵包店選購特色麵包及甜品，與Veronica在巴黎鐵塔下的戰神廣場野餐、打卡。Veronica預備的貝雷帽份外搶鏡，配戴時有甚麼需注意？她還分享打卡技巧。三人更拆解迷思，嘗試法國風味把牛角包浸泡咖啡來吃，會否中伏？兩位主持造訪巴黎最古老的糕點店及其姊妹朱古力店，試吃鎮店甜品「Rum baba」、朱古力放題……美食背後有甚麼故事？

programme.title: 鎮鄉之寶[粵/普]
programme.desc: 世界馳名的瑞士手錶，只佔全球產量2%，價值卻佔市場一半。本集君偉帶大家前往瑞士汝拉山脈，參觀鐘錶小鎮勒洛克勒，了解機械錶的歷史。然後認識掐絲琺瑯技藝，走訪製錶大師和維修及保養古董鐘的三父子，萬勿錯過。

programme.title: 夢想改造家[粵]
programme.desc: 節目突破以色彩和軟裝為主的傳統裝修形式，聚焦於空間改變和功能實現上。由頂尖設計師以有限的資金，在有限的空間裡，根據委託人的特殊需求進行徹底改造。通過設計師的匠心巧思，完成看似不可能的家裝夢想。

programme.title: 網紅甜卡[粵]
programme.desc: 法國女性時尚優雅，Christy、Jessica追尋當中不凡魅力，在Veronica引領下先到唇膏店，依個人膚色、衣著挑選不同顏色、質感、香味，打造個人專屬唇膏；再參觀香水品牌博物館，了解香水歷史，調配獨一無二專屬香水，增添女人味！兩位主持隨後拜會法國甜品網紅，學造「雲呢拿朱古力撻」，並以鏡頭捕捉甜品的誘惑，有什麼竅門？兩人又充當當地女攝影師的模特兒，在日照光影中的巴黎街頭，展現令人驚喜的靜態美。

programme.title: 娛樂新聞報道
programme.desc: 每晚緊貼香港娛樂圈的消息，以至世界各地的影視娛樂新聞，報道藝人最新動態、劇集和電影宣傳、演唱會精華、頒獎禮盛況等，甚至遠赴外地採訪娛樂盛事、追蹤各地影星，專訪觀眾熟悉的歌、影、視紅人，讓大家瞬間掌握影視娛樂圈的動態和最新消息。

programme.title: 不如食豪D[粵]
programme.desc: 歌手要突圍，歌藝、形象、談吐、營運社交平台都不可或缺！嘉賓泳兒近年發放暗黑魅力，更以「老火湯」形容自己？香港出生的泳兒在新加坡讀書多年，她最想念的是叻沙。尚友巧妙融合蒸水蛋與龍蝦叻沙，帶來不一樣滋味。想學唱歌的6號，即場接受泳兒測試，但頭幾粒音已走音！除了發洩扭龍蝦、「粗暴」打蛋，泳兒亦趁機向尚友學拋鑊。蒸水蛋想嫩滑無坑紋，要留意火候？比起下廚，原來泳兒愛藉洗碗減壓；她還趣談歌手好友的酒後百態。

programme.title: 玲玲友情報[粵]
programme.desc: 幻想一下，如死神突然降臨前，可安排家產分配，會怎樣分？J2ers答案足以引證彼此友誼！玲玲姐自言無子女，隨時分幾百萬給對她好之人？睇得劇多，玲玲姐對家人聆聽遺囑時的心情特別感興趣，嘉賓麥慶歡大狀竟稱毫無宣讀遺囑經驗？立遺囑不限年齡，卻宜結婚後才立，為甚麼？又聽聽嘉賓、主持帶來的遺產爭議，出現複雜的婚姻與家庭關係，各人可分幾多？律師都未必能提供肯定答案，或要待法庭裁斷，所以這集的結論是，記得立遺囑！

programme.title: 紅色高踭鞋#3[粵/韓][PG]
programme.desc: 小珍雅緊抱著貞國的遺體嚎啕大哭，祈求上帝讓爸爸活過來。赫相不顧金順反對，要和元配離婚，與熙瓊共組家庭。太吉敲詐赫相，拿到錢來給建煜做手術。玉璟對太吉的所為充滿罪惡感，決定自己撫養珍雅、珍鎬。

programme.title: Lifestyle - Gandhi's Footsteps
programme.desc: Gandhi’s philosophy of minimalism and non-violence won India's independence from the British Empire. Today, as India’s economy booms, his modern-day followers tell RTD that Gandhi’s principles are needed more than ever. These include a manager who runs barefoot, a Harley Davidson enthusiast who teaches school kids to share, and Gandhi’s last surviving staff member.

programme.title: Military and War - Theatre of War
programme.desc: DPR forces consists of many people who joined it in the special operation in Ukraine. There are miners, teachers, mechanics and even performers. Singers, dancers and musicians go to the frontlines to fight for their homeland. What is this conflict for such people with sophisticated nature, who faced combat and death? Watch in new Theatre of War.

programme.title: Society - Congo, My Precious
programme.desc: “Geological scandal” is a phrase often used to describe The Democratic Republic of Congo. It is one of the world’s most resource-rich countries with extensive deposits of gold, diamonds, tungsten and uranium amongst many others. The abundance of internationally valued minerals has however failed to bring any kind of prosperity. It began with colonial exploitation of the land and its people and continued in bloody civil war, the Congolese have harvested nothing from their country’s natural riches but misery and poverty.

programme.title: Society - Hero Wives
programme.desc: Ordinary Russian women from all corners of the country, volunteer to stand by their husbands fighting for Donbass liberation. They seize every opportunity to aid the defenders, sometimes even risking their own lives to personally deliver collected humanitarian aid directly to the frontlines. Their efforts do not only aid the fighters but also create precious moments for them to reunite with their husbands.

programme.title: Society - Killing Russian Culture
programme.desc: Since the beginning of the special operation in Ukraine, Russian people in the West have been up against the strongest wave of Russophobia which also engulfed Russian art and sport. Munich Philharmonic Orchestra cut all ties with Maestro Valery Gergiev and pianist Denis Matsuev found his name crossed out from the Carnegie Hall posters. Tolstoy, Dostoevsky and Chekhov are no longer welcome in the West, either. How does Russian culture withstand this wave of aggression?

programme.title: Newborn Russia - A fourth trip to the maternity ward for a 38-year-old mother - Newborn Russia (E19)
programme.desc: Alla is mother to a large family of 3 children with a fourth on the way. Although she has plenty of childbirth experience, her doctors have warned her that the fourth labour can be very unpredictable.

programme.title: Military and War - Ukraine's Arms Barons
programme.desc: As NATO injects billions of dollars into arming Ukraine, the scale of illegal weapons trafficking making its way out of Ukraine looms large. Consequently, bombs intended for the Ukrainian military are somehow spotted in Israel, and are also used by Mexican cartels on the U.S. border. The illicit trade dates back to 1991 when Ukraine gained independence. Our new documentary delves into the mysteries behind weaponry trafficking in modern Ukraine.

programme.title: Health - EVALI. Vapes of Death
programme.desc: To vape or not to vape? Is it safe? Is it safer than smoking regular cigarettes? There are more questions than answers about how vaping affects our health. Since 2019, cases of a mysterious vaping illness have become widespread. In the US alone, nearly 3,000 people were hospitalised between 2019 and 2020, and 68 died. The disease is now known as EVALI, short for e-cigarette, or vaping, product use-associated lung injury.

programme.title: Lifestyle - Dying to Dive
programme.desc: They can hold their breath for several minutes and slow their heart rate to almost nothing. Free divers plunge to incredible depths with no scuba gear. They push themselves to the limit to break new records but despite the serious risks involved, they can’t resist the call of the deep.

programme.title: Human Rights - Finnish Face of Fascism
programme.desc: During World War II, the Finnish army established a military administration in Karelia, one of the republics of the Soviet Union. For four years Soviet territory was occupied. Find out more in this thrilling story of 'Sumerian' and Zoya in our new documentary.

programme.title: Crime and Terrorism - Cyberscammers
programme.desc: As most services transferred online, scammers did the same. So now thieves don’t have to risk breaking into people’s houses. Instead, they can steal from the comfort of their own homes. In 2021, the damage inflicted by phone fraud in the US was estimated at almost $30 billion. But not everyone falls victim to the scammers. Some bloggers deliberately talk to scammers, record conversations, and ultimately expose them. So how does this business work on both sides?

programme.title: Newborn Russia - A fourth trip to the maternity ward for a 38-year-old mother - Newborn Russia (E19)
programme.desc: Alla is mother to a large family of 3 children with a fourth on the way. Although she has plenty of childbirth experience, her doctors have warned her that the fourth labour can be very unpredictable.

programme.title: Military and War - Ukraine's Arms Barons
programme.desc: As NATO injects billions of dollars into arming Ukraine, the scale of illegal weapons trafficking making its way out of Ukraine looms large. Consequently, bombs intended for the Ukrainian military are somehow spotted in Israel, and are also used by Mexican cartels on the U.S. border. The illicit trade dates back to 1991 when Ukraine gained independence. Our new documentary delves into the mysteries behind weaponry trafficking in modern Ukraine.

programme.title: Society - Afghanistan’s Loud, Mute Voices
programme.desc: Mahtab, a young deaf girl from Afghanistan, goes to school and dreams of becoming a surgeon. She also draws pictures to expose the poverty and injustice in her country in the hopes of attracting the world community’s attention to them. She is not alone in that endeavor. Other students of Nashinavayan, a special school for deaf people, also try to communicate their dreams and problems to the world through their art. They may not have a real physical voice, but the voice of their art is louder and more convincing than any words. Meet these outstanding young people and hear them out.

programme.title: Lifestyle - The Long Road To School
programme.desc: Like most students in rural Nepal, Durge Kami is a diligent pupil who tries to listen to his teachers. He differs from his school mates in just one respect, he is 69! At such a ripe old age, he was determined to realise his life’s ambition to complete his education. Not everyone supported him at first but by doing what he loves he’s become an inspiration for kids and adults alike.

programme.title: Newborn Russia - When mum comes to the rescue - Newborn Russia (E20)
programme.desc: Darima is looking forward to giving birth but as it will be her first time, she is blissfully unaware of how hard it can be. Nevertheless, she still thinks she’d like some support in the delivery room and asks her mother to be with her for the birth. Reluctantly, the mother agrees and proves an invaluable helper.

programme.title: Human Rights - Finnish Face of Fascism
programme.desc: During World War II, the Finnish army established a military administration in Karelia, one of the republics of the Soviet Union. For four years Soviet territory was occupied. During this time Finns built 14 concentration camps, 34 labor camps and dozens of prisons. The exact number of people who perished in Karelia and Petrozavodsk concentration camps is still unknown. In 1990, the concentration camp survivors united to find those responsible for the crimes. However, more than 30 years on, they continue to struggle for justice mainly to little avail.
